title: Episode 73: The Opioid Crisis with Janet Reilly
itunes:author: UW-Green Bay Psychology Department
itunes:summary: Our host, Ryan Martin is joined by Janet Reilly, a family Nurse Practitioner and Chair of MSN, Leadership & Management in Health Systems here at the University of Wisconsin-Green Bay. In this episode, they cover the opioid crisis- what it is, the potential causal mechanisms, and even the history of drug abuse!
